00:01:51.600 --> 00:01:53.690
is to feed you medicine.

9
00:01:54.160 --> 00:01:55.410
Piss off.

10
00:01:58.160 --> 00:02:00.010
What's wrong with you?

11
00:02:00.050 --> 00:02:00.690
Get out!

12
00:02:00.690 --> 00:02:01.160
Your Lordship.

13
00:02:01.160 --> 00:02:03.210
You asked me out?
