one can't make a big success
without being self-reliant?

882
00:40:36.700 --> 00:40:37.580
The position of consul

883
00:40:38.140 --> 00:40:39.460
is a big success.

884
00:40:40.620 --> 00:40:41.820
Although His Majesty

885
00:40:41.900 --> 00:40:43.060
