934
00:42:20.020 --> 00:42:21.060
Really?

935
00:42:28.340 --> 00:42:29.700
Listen, Ning Yuxuan.

936
00:42:29.700 --> 00:42:31.380
Don't try to scare me.

937
00:42:31.620 --> 00:42:32.580
I've already made

938
